<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/38315.Fooled_by_Randomness"><img alt="Fooled by Randomness: The Hidden Role of Chance in Life and in the Markets" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388180506l/38315._SX98_.jpg" />
